# `query`

This plugin defines the core behavior for queries which mostly
involves establishing subscriptions to the cache and accumulating
variables.

- Type: `ClientPlugin`

```typescript:title=src/client.ts
import { HoudiniClient } from '$houdini'
import { query } from '$houdini/plugins'

export default new HoudiniClient({
    url: "...",
    pipeline: [
        query
    ]
})
```
